PREREQUISITES
-------------
The RF24 library by TMRh20 (https://github.com/TMRh20/RF24) must be compiled and installed first.

HOW TO COMPILE
--------------
ardu-ir:
    g++ -lrf24-bcm ardu-ir.cpp Keeloq.cpp -o ardu-ir

ardu-temp:
    g++ -lrf24-bcm ardu-temp.cpp -o ardu-temp

